      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUNGLE HOLLIE (6) was below best last time when sixth but prior to that was a Mix winner in quick time at this track. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Has the ability and expected to bounce back. BEES HIVE (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Exorbitant (30.45) in a Grade 5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to feature again. SMART AUSSIE (1) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (30.46) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Richmond. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings six times from eight attempts. Key runner on best form. WOW ACE (2) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this circuit.",
